While this game has been amazing for years their support team has not. Their ban detection is so old that you CAN in fact get a false positive. Even if it is very rare. EVScape was a perfect example. And he was LIVE STREAMING.

If you DO get one then it’s completely over. They reject your appeals, are firm in their stance believing that their system is impervious to faults, and any money you’ve spent on this game is just completely gone.

DO NOT listen to any “mod” that responds to these reviews either. They just regurgitate copy paste crap about ban appeals and don’t  pay attention to the fact that you already appealed (nor do they mention that you only get 1 appeal chance on an automated system)...

Think very carefully about how you want to support this company. You are ALWAYS at risk no matter how small the chance may be. If you wish to play this amazing game I heavily recommend having the time to get membership in-game with gold and bonds and NOT through your credit card.
